"subtopic": "1. Two Types Of Glands",
"content": "There are two types of glands in our body - exocrine glands and endocrine glands\n\n• Hormones acts as messengers and coordinate different functions in our body.\n• Through the blood, secretions of endocrine glands are carried to the target organs.\n• Of endocrine glands are called hormones.\n• Hormones are secreted in extremely small quantities.\n• Increase or decrease in the hormone secretion is harmful for an organism.",
